    "ideation": "This animation personifies the rhythmic physical effort and momentum of operating a manual wheelchair. Rather than focusing on the chair itself, the face becomes the engine. The 'push' cycle is represented by eyes that exert effort (squinting and looking down at the wheels) followed by a lift and glide (widening and looking up as momentum is gained). The mouth acts as the mechanical rhythm of the wheels: a rolling wave that accelerates and stabilizes. The color palette uses a determined burnt orange and a steady, reliable slate blue to represent athletic resolve and the metallic nature of the equipment.",
